text: The restaurant interior is calmly understated. Service is efficient, knowledgeable about the dishes, and very friendly. The food, though, is clearly the star here. All the dishes sampled were absolutely gorgeous and delicious. Portions were perfectly sized. Overall, an excellent experience.

They do serve food, and its good. It offers both middle eastern and western food and the party begins when the music comes on. Though there are some restrictions now, which I dont understand, but the food here is quite good and I would visit for a change.
